@node Note

 0.  Note :


   If your screen is filled with sTrAnGe  C O L O U R S , don't be afraid :

   =>   press the right mouse button and they will disappear !!!! 

   This is done by SpeedLoad to show you that you have done something 
   WRONG  ( a wrong path, modified something you shouldn't ... :-))
   and it allows you to check on what is wrong in order to make it work .


